<p>John and Dave kick off this first Premium episode of October with lots of goodies, including discussing some creative ways to sync calendars, the best practices for nuking &amp; paving your Mac, plus some listener comments about using Windows-only webcams on the Mac, as well as a great comment about softare AND hardware issues.&nbsp;</p>
<p>If you&rsquo;re not already a susbscriber, why not become one today to get instant access to this episode and support your two favorite geeks.</p>
